        </section>

        <section class="section-4">
            <div class="container-book">
                <div class="left-column-book">
                    <!-- Hình ảnh của bạn -->
                    <img src="~/images/book.gif" />
                </div>
                <div class="right-column-book">
                    <p>Drenched in a rich tapestry of history and culture, the ____________ stands as a testament to the enduring spirit of human civilization, seamlessly interweaving time-honored traditions with the forefront of technological advancements.</p>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <button id="a">City</button>
                        <button id="an">Landscape</button>
                    </div>
                    <p>The advancement of modern technology has revolutionized the way we communicate, making it easier for people to stay connected across_______distances.</p>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <button id="an">History</button>
                        <button id="a">Geographical </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-question">
            <div class="title-question">Các dạng bài tập</div>
        </section>
        <section class="horizontal-section">
            <div class="horizontal-box">
                Demonstrating his culinary skills, Mark ____________ a delicious three-course meal for the dinner party.
                <p>A. Prepares</p>
                <p>B. Prepared</p>
            </div>
            <div class="horizontal-box">
                Critics praised the artist for the ____________ and originality displayed in his latest masterpiece
                <p>A. Creativity</p>
                <p>B. Diligence</p>
            </div>
            <div class="horizontal-box">
                Although his both legs were broken in the crash, he managed to get out of the car before it exploded
                <p>Rewrite: Despite his ____</p>
            </div>
